a-terbaru-kasus-positif-corona-jadi-450-bertambah-81|title=Data Terbaru: Kasus Positif Corona Jadi 450, Bertambah 81|last=detikcom|first=Tim|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-21}}</ref>\n\n====22 March====\n* [[:id:Ikatan Dokter Indonesia|Indonesia Medical Association]] (IDI) announced 6 doctors (dr Toni Daniel Silitonga; dr Ucok Martin SpP; dr Djoko Judodjoko, SpB; dr Hadio Ali SpS; dr Laurentius P, SpKJ; dr Adi Mirsaputra SpTHT) have contracted COVID-19.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://health.detik.com/berita-detikhealth/d-4949139/6-dokter-indonesia-jadi-korban-pandemi-corona-ini-daftarnya|title=6 Dokter Indonesia Jadi Korban Pandemi Corona, Ini Daftarnya|last=Mahardhika|first=Anjar|website=detikHealth|language=id|access-date=2020-03-22}}</ref>\n* Indonesia announced 64 new cases, a total of 514 cases. Indonesia also announced 29 recovered and 48 deaths.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4949042/pernyataan-lengkap-pemerintah-soal-514-kasus-corona-per-22-maret|title=Pernyataan Lengkap Pemerintah soal 514 Kasus Corona Per 22 Maret|last=Permana|first=Rakhmad Hidayatulloh|website=detiknews|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref> An increase of 10 deaths with a death rate of 9.33%, which was the biggest death rate so far.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4949055/pasien-corona-meninggal-48-orang-tingkat-kematian-jadi-93|title=Pasien Corona Meninggal 48 Orang, Tingkat Kematian Jadi 9,3%|last=Permana|first=Rakhmad Hidayatulloh|website=detiknews|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref>\n\n====23 March====\n* Indonesia announced 65 new cases, bringing the total to 579 cases. Indonesia also announced 30 recovered and 49 deaths.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4950124/per-23-maret-kasus-positif-corona-di-indonesia-jadi-579|title=Per 23 Maret, Kasus Positif Corona di Indonesia Jadi 579|last=Ibrahim|first=Gibran Maulana|website=detiknews|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref>\n*President Joko Widodo inaugurated the first COVID-19 makeshift hospital in the country at the [[Kemayoran Athletes Village|former athlete's village for the 2018 Asian Games]] in [[Kemayoran]], Jakarta. It was slated to be fitted with 3000 beds for patients requiring isolation.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2020/03/23/09435921/presiden-jokowi-resmikan-rs-darurat-corona-di-wisma-atlet-kemayoran|title=Presiden Jokowi Resmikan RS Darurat Corona di Wisma Atlet Kemayoran|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|website=KOMPAS.com|language=id|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://finance.detik.com/berita-ekonomi-bisnis/d-4949291/dipermak-jadi-rs-hari-ini-wisma-atlet-siap-diisi-pasien-corona|title=Dipermak Jadi RS, Hari Ini Wisma Atlet Siap Diisi Pasien Corona|last=Hamdani|first=Trio|website=detikfinance|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref> Later reports suggested that it would house only 1,800 beds for the first phase.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/as-testing-expands-patients-at-indonesias-athletes-village-turn-hospital-expected-to|title=As coronavirus testing expands, cases at Indonesia's athlete's village-turned-hospital expected to rise dramatically|last=hermesauto|date=2020-03-25|website=The Straits Times|language=en|access-date=2020-03-25}}</ref>\n\n====24 March====\n* President Joko Widodo announced the cancellation of the annual national examination (''[[National Exam (Indonesia)|Ujian Nasional]]'') for all education levels, except Vocational High School (''Sekolah Menengah Kejuruan, SMK'') that has been done in almost half of all schools in the country.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4951217/jokowi-putuskan-tiadakan-un-2020-imbas-corona|title=Jokowi Putuskan Tiadakan UN 2020 Imbas Corona|last=detikcom|first=Tim|website=detiknews|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tirto.id/murid-smk-sudah-telanjur-un-nadiem-maaf-kalau-kalian-kecewa-eHlA|title=Murid SMK S