an 19 Meninggal|last=detikcom|first=Tim|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref> The 19 fatalities mean that Indonesia has now recorded the highest death toll among Southeast Asian countries hit by the coronavirus to date.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2020/03/18/covid-19-indonesia-records-highest-death-toll-in-southeast-asia-at-19.html|title=COVID-19: Indonesia records highest death toll in Southeast Asia at 19|last=Post|first=The Jakarta|website=The Jakarta Post|language=en|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref> Indonesia's case fatality rate has reached 8.37% which is double the world case fatality rate (4.07%).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4944800/tingkat-kematian-pasien-corona-di-ri-837-bagaimana-negara-lain|title=Tingkat Kematian Pasien Corona di RI 8,37%, Bagaimana Negara Lain?|last=Damarjati|first=Danu|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref>\n*7 Indonesians in [[India]] tested positive for COVID-19 were a part of a 10-member team who travelled to [[Karimnagar]] for a religious tour.<ref name=\"TH1\">{{cite news |last1=Geetanath |first1=K. Shiva Shankar & V. |title=Coronavirus {{!}} Telangana reports 8 new COVID-19 cases |url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/telangana-reports-8-new-covid-19-cases/article31102733.ece?homepage=true |newspaper=The Hindu |language=en-IN |date=19 March 2020}}</ref>\n*After 2 positive cases, Governor of West Kalimantan [[Sutarmidji]] declares an \"extraordinary event\" until further notice.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4944658/ada-2-kasus-positif-gubernur-tetapkan-kalbar-klb-corona|title=Ada 2 Kasus Positif, Gubernur Tetapkan Kalbar KLB Corona|last=Kholid|first=Idham|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n\n====19 March====\n* Joko Widodo announces 7 critical points (mass rapid tests, incentive for medical personnel, involve religious people, stop exporting medical equipment, stop holiday, incentive for small and medium enterprises, increase food stocks) to accelerate the elimination of COVID-19 outbreak in Indonesia.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4945259/ini-arahan-lengkap-terbaru-jokowi-untuk-tangani-virus-corona|title=Ini Arahan Lengkap Terbaru Jokowi untuk Tangani Virus Corona|last=detikcom|first=Tim|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=LIVE : Rapat Terbatas Laporan Tim Gugus Tugas COVID-19, Istana Merdeka, 19 Maret 2020|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NnpUlfKq74U|language=en|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2020/03/19/15282081/7-arahan-terbaru-jokowi-untuk-penanganan-covid-19|title=7 Arahan Terbaru Jokowi untuk Penanganan Covid-19 Halaman all|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|website=Kompas.com|language=id|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n*Indonesia announced 82 new cases, bringing the total to 309 cases.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2020/03/19/15531171/update-total-pasien-covid-19-di-indonesia-kini-309-kasus|title=UPDATE: Total Pasien Covid-19 di Indonesia Kini 309 Kasus|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|website=Kompas.com|language=id|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4945783/kasus-wni-positif-corona-melonjak-dari-227-jadi-309|title=Kasus WNI Positif Corona Melonjak dari 227 Jadi 309|last=Sidik|first=Farih Maulana|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref> However, it is revised to 308 cases.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbcindonesia.com/news/20200319182124-4-146252/pemerintah-meralat-kasus-positif-corona-di-ri-jadi-308-kasus|title=Pemerintah Meralat: Kasus Positif Corona di RI Jadi 308 Kasus|last=dob|website=news|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref>\n*4 more patients in DKI Jakarta announced cured from COVID-19.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2020/03/19/16104301/update-15-orang-dinyatakan-sembuh-dari-cov