 5 February: \n** [[Haikou]] and [[Sanya]], Hainan;<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://m.21jingji.com/article/20200205/herald/d24c879bfb8f1c2f6cab5d56b1cf558b.html|script-title=zh:\u6d77\u5357\u6d77\u53e3\u3001\u4e09\u4e9a\u5bf9\u6240\u6709\u6751\u5e84\u3001\u5c0f\u533a\u7b49\u5b9e\u884c\u5c01\u95ed\u5f0f\u7ba1\u7406}}</ref> \n** [[Kunming]], Yunnan; \n** [[Qingdao]], [[Jinan]], [[Tai'an]], and [[Rizhao]], Shandong; \n** [[Nanchang]], Jiangxi; \n** [[Hefei]], Anhui; \n** [[Nanning]], Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region; \n** [[Shijiazhuang]], Hebei; \n** [[Yangzhou]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.yangtse.com/zncontent/256477.html|script-title=zh:\u626c\u5dde\uff1a\u6240\u6709\u6751\u5e84\u3001\u5c0f\u533a\u3001\u4f01\u4e1a\u3001\u5355\u4f4d\u5b9e\u884c\u5c01\u95ed\u5f0f\u7ba1\u7406|script-work=zh:\u626c\u5b50\u665a\u62a5|accessdate=8 February 2020}}</ref> [[Taizhou, Jiangsu|Taizhou]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.taizhou.gov.cn/art/2020/2/5/art_392_2648061.html|script-title=zh:\u5173\u4e8e\u4e25\u683c\u75ab\u60c5\u9632\u63a7\u671f\u95f4\u4eba\u5458\u7ba1\u63a7\u7684\u901a\u544a\uff08\u7b2c7\u53f7\uff09|publisher=Taizhou, Jiangsu People's Government |accessdate=9 February 2020}}</ref> [[Suqian]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xichu.net/news/redian/2020/02/2020-02-07452112.html|script-title=zh:\u5bbf\u8fc1\u5e02\u6700\u65b0\u901a\u544a|script-website=zh:\u897f\u695a\u7f51|accessdate=9 February 2020}}</ref> and [[Funing County, Jiangsu|Funing County]], Yancheng,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://funing.yancheng.gov.cn/art/2020/2/7/art_6617_3322158.html|script-title=zh:\u5173\u4e8e\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u52a0\u5f3a\u75ab\u60c5\u9632\u63a7\u671f\u95f4\u5c0f\u533a\u7ba1\u7406\u7684\u901a\u544a|publisher=Funing County, Jiangsu People's Government |accessdate=11 February 2020}}</ref> Jiangsu.\n\n* 6 February: \n** [[Liaoning]]; \n** [[Jiangxi]];<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldjournal.com/6771085/article-%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%8D%E9%80%B2%E9%9A%8E%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%81%E7%9C%81%E